1.5 TEXT GENERATION WEBUI (Oobabooga / textgen-webui)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Default Port:       7860 (Gradio web UI)
API Port:           5000 (blocking API) / 5005 (streaming API)
                    7861 (sometimes used as API port in newer versions)
HTTP Server:        Gradio (UI), custom Python HTTP server (API)

Key API Endpoints:
  POST /api/v1/generate           -> text generation (KoboldAI-compatible)
  POST /api/v1/chat               -> chat generation
  POST /api/v1/stop-stream        -> stop ongoing stream
  GET  /api/v1/model              -> current model info
  POST /api/v1/model              -> load a model
  GET  /api/v1/token-count        -> count tokens
  POST /v1/chat/completions       -> OpenAI-compat (if --api flag used)
  POST /v1/completions            -> OpenAI-compat
  GET  /v1/models                 -> OpenAI-compat model list
  GET  /                          -> Gradio web UI (HTML response)

Banner Fingerprints:
  - Gradio HTML on port 7860
  - /api/v1/generate endpoint with KoboldAI-style request body
  - Server headers contain "gradio" or Python HTTP server

