1.6 KOBOLDCPP
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Default Port:       5001 (TCP)
HTTP Server:        Python-based HTTP server

Key API Endpoints:
  GET  /                          -> Web UI (HTML)
  POST /api/v1/generate           -> KoboldAI-compatible text generation
  GET  /api/v1/model              -> current model info
  GET  /api/v1/config/max_length  -> max context length
  GET  /api/v1/config/max_context_length -> context window config
  GET  /api/v1/info/version       -> KoboldCpp version
  GET  /api/extra/version         -> extended version info
  POST /api/extra/generate/stream -> streaming generation
  POST /api/extra/tokencount      -> token counting
  POST /v1/chat/completions       -> OpenAI-compat (if enabled)
  GET  /v1/models                 -> OpenAI-compat model list

Banner Fingerprints:
  - Port 5001 with /api/v1/generate responding to KoboldAI-style JSON
  - /api/extra/ path prefix unique to KoboldCpp

