1.10 ANYTHINGLLM
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Default Port:       3001 (TCP) — desktop app API
HTTP Server:        Express.js (Node.js)

Key API Endpoints:
  GET  /api/ping                  -> {"online":true}
  POST /api/v1/workspace/:slug/chat -> chat with a workspace
  GET  /api/v1/workspaces         -> list workspaces
  GET  /api/v1/system             -> system info
  GET  /api/v1/auth               -> check authentication
  POST /api/v1/auth/login         -> login (returns JWT)
  GET  /api/docs                  -> Swagger UI

Banner Fingerprints:
  - /api/ping returning {"online":true}
  - /api/v1/workspace/:slug/chat URL pattern is unique

