1.11 HuggingFace TEXT GENERATION INFERENCE (TGI)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Default Port:       80 (Docker deployment, internally 80)
  Alternate:        8080, 3000
HTTP Server:        Rust-based Actix server

Key API Endpoints:
  GET  /                          -> {"error":"Not Found"} or 200 JSON
  GET  /health                    -> empty 200 response
  GET  /info                      -> model info JSON (model_id, model_dtype, etc.)
  POST /generate                  -> text generation (TGI native format)
  POST /generate_stream           -> streaming generation (SSE)
  POST /v1/chat/completions       -> OpenAI-compat chat
  POST /v1/completions            -> OpenAI-compat text
  GET  /v1/models                 -> model list
  GET  /metrics                   -> Prometheus metrics
  GET  /docs                      -> Swagger UI (custom Rust swagger)

Banner Fingerprints:
  - /info returns fields: model_id, model_dtype, model_sha, max_total_tokens
  - /generate uses inputs/parameters format (not OpenAI messages format)
  - Docker image signature in /info: docker_label field

